Guys guys guys! We got this answer on the LAS forums from one of the rioters:

&quot;Los skins de Slayers y Zombies son tematicos de Halloween, ciertamente, pero no son nuestro contenido de Harrowing de este a&ntilde;o. :)
Paciencia! Ya vienen mas cosas.&quot;

Translation:

&quot;Slayers and Zombies skins are Halloween themed, certainly, but they&#039;re not this year&#039;s Harrowing content.
Patience! More things are coming.&quot;

replies.body:
@Riot please beta test theme's to reduce confusion.

Well those slayer skins really aren't in the spirit of halloween, slasher flicks maybe? But a lot of people are dissapointed that the theme isn't very recognizable and focused entirely in a mature blood (and gore-eque?) subset. 

I don't find the slayers appealing personally and I don't the halloween in them either. Zombie nunu looks really nice, but I'm happy with my TPA nunu because I haven't played him much as a jungle main with vi and zac dominating my picks.
